<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1012,1253]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,466,1084,1109]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540">Species identification.</emphasis>
The collection of Herrich-Schäffer is lost (H. Nickel, personal communication). Identification of this species is based on 
<bibRefCitation author="Fieber" box="[613,767,1119,1144]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" refString="Fieber, F. X. (1868) Europaische neue oder wenig bekannte Bythoscopida. Verhandlungen der Kaiserlich-Koniglichen Zoologisch-botanischen Gesellschaft in Wien, 18, 449 - 464." type="journal article" year="1868">
Fieber (
<number box="[700,758,1119,1144]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" value="1868.0">1868</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Ribaut" box="[823,981,1119,1144]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" refString="Ribaut, H. (1952) Homopteres Auchenorhynques. II (Jassidae). Faune de France, 57, 1 - 474." type="journal article" year="1952">
Ribaut (
<number box="[914,972,1119,1144]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" value="1952.0">1952</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and on investigation of specimens from Bavaria collected by Dr. H. Nickel ca. 
<quantity box="[585,670,1156,1181]" metricMagnitude="5" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" unit="km" value="150.0">150 km</quantity>
North-West of the 
<typeStatus box="[885,933,1157,1181]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540">type</typeStatus>
locality (Figs. 
<number box="[1103,1174,1156,1181]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" value="11.35">11, 35</number>
, 
<number box="[1186,1258,1156,1180]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" value="38.8">
38, 
<number box="[1228,1258,1156,1180]" pageId="3" pageNumber="540" value="80.1">80</number>
</number>
, 100).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
